
1  

“Abu ketutuk aitutuket kakonyeka;

Aso ti kapedo biai asesen apese?


2  Naarai akorakinet anyoin naka Edeke naebuni kokuju,

airumet nanyoin da naka Lokapedor kere naebuni kokuju?


3  Mam kereka erai epola mama ejai yenimam edolit,

ka abili da mama ejaas luiswamaete numam adolit?


4  

Mam kereka ŋes eseseni ikarotin,

imari da akailameta kere?


5  “Arai kiupanara kaamameak,

arai da ewonyarito akakeje aiŋal,


6  (Mere ketemi kaitemis naerian, tetere ejenuni Edeke abeiteka!)


7  

arai epaarit akakeju korot,

ka ekatau da arai abu kotupa akakonye,

ido arai iminaikina aitakinet kere akaninika;


8  aso mere kaye, konyam ice,

eebo, korutoi inyamat lukomanikorika.


9  “Arai ecodara ekatau mama ejai aberu,

arai da aperunit eoŋ kokek loka eidunyeteka:


10  aso kirieik akaberu ice,

ido kirukumete ŋes.


11  Naarai tierai ŋin naketal,

eebo, tierai aronis naibusakinit ikatubok aitican;


12  naarai erai akim naidopori kiton Amudiario,

ido naekoto arutor eiyasika kere.


13  “Arai abu kamen akirot naka ekakejaanakinan arai naka akakejaanakinan,

naketepeseniata,


14  aso ekwaikini ai arai kenyou Edeke?

Nakabunokinia, aboŋokini biai?


15  

Lokasubi eoŋ kotoma akoik mere ŋes kesubi ŋes da?

Mere ediopet lokiluŋuluŋuuni oni kakoik?


16  “Arai abu kemik lukican yenimielas,

arai abu kesiriono akonye nuka apuserut;


17  arai abu kanyam bon akatap,

komam ekoki enyamit;


18  (Konye mere, ageun keiditeuka kipoloi keoŋ kwape kaneejai papa,

abu karai ekeŋarenikinonike ageun kakoik naka totoka.)


19  Arai abu kaany yenetwani kanuka amamus inapen,

arai yenilwaritoi komamei yenikimukis;


20  arai aŋabeteke mam kemalat,

ido arai mam emwanunit kajulo nuka amerekekika;


21  arai abu kario akakan mama ejai ikoki,

naarai abu kaany aigaŋio korute:


22  kosodi kigwegweun ekeperika kolagagamit,

kobila da akoit naka akanika.


23  Naarai abu kakuriana epola loebuni kama ejai Edeke,

ido kanuka akepolou mam nuabu kapedo aswam.


24  “Arai abu kamunokin esabu,

arai da abu katema esabu loejok ebe, ‘Ijo amunonutuka.’


25  Arai abu kesiyalamik akabar naapol noi,

naarai akeriana akakan;


26  

arai abu kasesen akoloŋ naecai,

arai elap loelosi iliyai;


27  kosodi ekatau aijodoorio kaiyeiyea,

akaituk da konu akanika:


28  

Ŋin da tierai aronis naibusakinit ikatubok aitican,

naarai tikeŋala Edeke loejai toma akuj.


29  “Arai abu kesiyalamik amudiar naka ŋol kalokalai,

arai abu kekeu nakedoloki ŋes aronis;


30  

(Eebo, mam abu kacam akaituk adiakar,

toma ailip akeijar elama.)


31  Ituŋa lukowemaka arai mam apotu kotemasi atiar,

“Iŋai epedori adumun ituŋanan yenimam imonikin ikenyamat?


32  

Mam ipejonon aperenenei orot;

konye abu kaŋaanakini ikaloton ikakekia;


33  Arai abu karap aidiakaka kwape Adam,

kanuka aibwa numam adoliteka kotoma atorobuka;


34  

naarai abu kayoŋ atukot naepol,

kakurianar amwaŋio naka ikekia,

tape eliliŋi komam alomari kiŋa—


35  Wu okwe arai kejai yenikapupi!

(Koany, na ŋes aanyuneteka, kaboŋok eoŋ Lokapedor kere!)

Arai kiŋa keoŋ ŋin naewadikat lokasurupika aiwosa eoŋ!


36  Abeit tikarioŋ kokeperika,

tikaenik kwape kaboke.”


37  Tikabilaki ŋes aimwaus naka akailameta,

tikekunyaki neejai ŋesi kwape lokapolon.


38  “Arai apotu alupoka kiworoto aitepesen eoŋ,

ibwololoete da aloboikec nepepe;


39  arai abu kanyam akeceraito komam aitac,

arai bo abu kedosilana ikulepek,


40  kobwaŋut ikukwa aibois naka akima,

ka igitun aibois naka esairi.”

Asana ne akiro nuka Yob.

